KeysToMetaData.PremierDivisions_Description: Premier division is determined by the average of the top 5 players' MMR on the team.  Play your first match to lock in your division.  Win playoff tournaments to promote to higher divisions.
KeysToMetaData.PremierDivisions_ContenderEligibility_De: is given to players who are ranked Immortal 3 or higher; have played a Weekly or Playoff match on a team with Contender or Invite; or have earned a "Playoff Team", "Finalist", or "Winner" Crest in Elite 5 or higher.
